        While activity is decreasing, the 2008-2009 flu season is not=
 over, according to the CDC.
        http://www.cdc.gov/flu/weekly/

      =
  As of last week: "Nine states reported regional activity; 17 states repor=
ted local influenza activity; the District of Columbia and 22 states report=
ed sporadic influenza activity; and two states reported no influenza activi=
ty."

        So at the moment, if you have symptoms, it is not likely to b=
e swine flu.
